author: MATTHEW LEE AP Diplomatic Writer
title: G-7 foreign ministers spar over coronavirus amid pandemic
description: Foreign ministers from the Group of 7 leading industrialized democracies have sparred over whether to call out China as the source of the coronavirus pandemic
content:
WASHINGTON -- 
Foreign ministers from the Group of 7 leading industrialized democracies sparred Wednesday over whether to call out China as the source of the coronavirus pandemic.
